{"title_page": "Kerstlingerode", "text_new": "[[File:DEU Kerstlingerode COA.svg|right|100px]]\n''Kerstlingerode'' is a village in the municipality (''Gemeinde'') [[Gleichen]] in the district [[G\u00f6ttingen]], [[Germany]].  It lies on L569 between [[Beienrode]] and [[Rittmarshausen]], about ten kilometers south-east of G\u00f6ttingen. The village of 245 residents (as of December 31, 2010)<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.gleichen.de/staticsite/staticsite.php?menuid=29&topmenu=19|title =Rundreise durch die Gemeinde Gleichen - Kerstlingerode|date = |accessdate = 2014-07-12|website = |publisher = Gemeinde Gleichen|last = |first = }}</ref> is primarily agricultural.   There is one church and the largest school in the municipality.<ref>[http://www.gleichen.de/kerstlingerode/home.htm Das bietet Kerstlingerode<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>  There is a volunteer fire department <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ffw-kerstlingerode.de/2.html |title=Freiwillige Feuerwehr Kerstlingerode - Wir \u00fcber uns<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090614052257/http://www.ffw-kerstlingerode.de/2.html |archive-date=2009-06-14 |url-status=dead }}</ref> and a wind-instrument band. The village mayor is Claudia Schuppe-Bl\u00f6dow.\n\n==History==\nThe community was once known as ''Burg Kerstlingerode''.  It is said to have been founded in AD 1100.<ref>[http://www.beepworld.de/members2/wjahns/beienrode.htm Beienrode<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050910012414/http://www.beepworld.de/members2/wjahns/beienrode.htm |date=2005-09-10 }}</ref>\n\nIn 1408 the knight of Bischoffshausen laid waste to some of the lands of Kerstlingerode.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://worldroots.com/brigitte/royal/bischoffshausenburg.htm |title=Worldroots.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704083959/http://worldroots.com/brigitte/royal/bischoffshausenburg.htm |archive-date=2008-07-04 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nIn 1925 and 1933, the population was recorded as being 315 people.  In 1939 it was 307.<ref>[http://www.verwaltungsgeschichte.de/goettingen.html#ew33gttkerstlingrde Deutsche Verwaltungsgeschichte Provinz Hannover, Kreis G\u00f6ttingen<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\n<!--   Otto von K. seems to have been a man of import, and presumably the knight of the Burg.  The family died out in 1641 or so, with Christoph's death.-->\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.gleichen.de/kerstlingerode/home.htm]\n\n== References ==\n\n<references/>\n\n{{coord|51|28|N|10|06|E|display=title|region:DE_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Lower Saxony]]\n\n\n{{G\u00f6ttingen-geo-stub}}\n\n[[de:Gleichen#Gemeindegliederung]]\n", "text_old": "[[File:DEU Kerstlingerode COA.svg|right|100px]]\n''Kerstlingerode'' is a village in the municipality (''Gemeinde'') [[Gleichen]] in the district [[G\u00f6ttingen]], [[Germany]].  It lies on L569 between [[Beienrode]] and [[Rittmarshausen]], about ten kilometers south-east of G\u00f6ttingen. The village of 245 residents (as of December 31, 2010)<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.gleichen.de/staticsite/staticsite.php?menuid=29&topmenu=19|title =Rundreise durch die Gemeinde Gleichen - Kerstlingerode|date = |accessdate = 2014-07-12|website = |publisher = Gemeinde Gleichen|last = |first = }}</ref> is primarily agricultural.   There is one church and the largest school in the municipality.<ref>[http://www.gleichen.de/kerstlingerode/home.htm Das bietet Kerstlingerode<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>  There is a volunteer fire department <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ffw-kerstlingerode.de/2.html |title=Freiwillige Feuerwehr Kerstlingerode - Wir \u00fcber uns<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090614052257/http://www.ffw-kerstlingerode.de/2.html |archive-date=2009-06-14 |url-status=dead }}</ref> and a wind-instrument band. The village mayor is Claudia Schuppe-Bl\u00f6dow.\n\n==History==\nThe community was once known as ''Burg Kerstlingerode''.  It is said to have been founded in AD 1100.<ref>[http://www.beepworld.de/members2/wjahns/beienrode.htm Beienrode<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050910012414/http://www.beepworld.de/members2/wjahns/beienrode.htm |date=2005-09-10 }}</ref>\n\nIn 1408 the knight of Bischoffshausen laid waste to some of the lands of Kerstlingerode.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://worldroots.com/brigitte/royal/bischoffshausenburg.htm |title=Worldroots.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704083959/http://worldroots.com/brigitte/royal/bischoffshausenburg.htm |archive-date=2008-07-04 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nIn 1925 and 1933, the population was recorded as being 315 people.  In 1939 it was 307.<ref>[http://www.verwaltungsgeschichte.de/goettingen.html#ew33gttkerstlingrde Deutsche Verwaltungsgeschichte Provinz Hannover, Kreis G\u00f6ttingen<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\n<!--   Otto von K. seems to have been a man of import, and presumably the knight of the Burg.  The family died out in 1641 or so, with Christoph's death.-->\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.gleichen.de/kerstlingerode/home.htm]\n\n== References ==\n\n<references/>\n\n{{coord|51|28|N|10|06|E|display=title|region:DE_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Lower Saxony]]\n\n\n{{G\u00f6ttingen-geo-stub}}\n\n[[de:Gleichen#Gemeindegliederung]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerstlingerode"}
