ael Arc\u00e1ngel]]\n|[[File:Mission San Rafael Arc\u00e1ngel, San Rafael CA USA -The reconstructed capilla (chapel) at Mission San Rafael Arc\u00e1ngel - panoramio.jpg|100px]]\n|1104 5th Ave, [[San Rafael, California|San Rafael]]\n|Founded in 1817 as a medical asistencia (\"sub-mission\") of [[Mission San Francisco de As\u00eds]]; granted full mission status in 1822.<ref>{{cite web|title=San Rafael Arc\u00e1ngel Key Facts|publisher=California Missions|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://missionscalifornia.com/san-rafael-arcangel-mission/key-facts}}</ref>\n|-\n|Our Lady of Loretto\n|\n|1806 Novato Boulevard, [[Novato, California|Novato]]\n|Parish dates to 1892 as a mission church; current church dedicated in 1963<ref>{{cite web|title=Parish History|publisher=Our Lady of Loretto|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://ollnovato.org/parish-history}}</ref>\n|-\n|Our Lady of Mount Carmel\n|[[File:Our Lady of Mount Carmel, Mill Valley (2012).jpg|100px]]\n|3 Oakdale Avenue, [[Mill Valley, California|Mill Valley]]\n|Current church dedicated in 1968<ref>{{cite web|title=About Us|publisher=Our Lady of Mount Carmel Catholic Church|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://mountcarmelmv.org/pb/wp_1ad20e0c/wp_1ad20e0c.html}}</ref>\n|-\n|Sacred Heart\n|\n|10189 State Route, #1, [[Olema, California|Olema]]\n|Current church dedicated in 1967<ref>{{cite web|title=History of Sacred Heart Parish and Sacred Heart Church|publisher=Sacred Heart Parish|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=http://www.marinsacredheart.com/about.html}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Anselm\n|\n|97 Shady Lane and Bolinas, [[San Anselmo, California|San Anselmo]]\n|Parish established and church built in 1908<ref>{{cite web|title=Our History|publisher=Saint Anselm Catholic Church|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://saintanselm.org/about-our-parish/our-history/}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Anthony of Padua\n|\n|1000 Cambridge Street, Novato\n|Parish established 1968; church dedicated 1971<ref>{{cite web|title=History of Saint Anthony of Padua Chu